            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%231%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E9%AA%A8%E7%9B%86%E5%89%8D%E5%80%BE%23&amp;extparam=%231%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E9%AA%A8%E7%9B%86%E5%89%8D%E5%80%BE%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#1个动作缓解骨盆前倾#</span></a>】骨盆前倾会造成一系列肌群改变，导致小腹突出，让一些看起来并不胖的人，也会有小肚子。一招教你拉伸髂腰肌，缓解骨盆前倾👇🏻每次3分钟，每天2次，周末宅家也可以练起来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[打工人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a1/2023_earner_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>~（北大医院骨科孙浩林医生）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4830742073770034" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1h7os6ix9c4j60u01hctd502.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Ru6J3w8Llx080qdatJxe01041200bKuY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690789806&amp;ssig=wK6ZnJ8Oru&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ARrYc9b6lx080qdc53Co010412006w0k0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690789806&amp;ssig=u5bHrESu7O&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/h94F4PmYlx080qdbmSRO010412003kMl0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690789806&amp;ssig=oYSBtNg01C&amp;KID=unistore,vi